# Feeds Configuration

413 RSS feeds for daily news digest.

## Categories

- `AI/` - AI/ML news
- `GENERAL/` - General tech news
- `EVENTS/` - Events and conferences
- `ALERT/` - Security alerts
- `ACGN/` - Anime, Comics, Games, Novels (future)

## Format

```json
{
  "feeds": [
    {
      "url": "https://example.com/rss",
      "name": "Example Blog",
      "category": "GENERAL",
      "reliability": 0.9,
      "enabled": true
    }
  ]
}
```
